<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Information About Nepal 🇳🇵</title>

    <!-- Main CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

    <!-- Leaflet Map CSS (NEW) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet/dist/leaflet.css">

</head>


<body>


<!-- ================= Hero Section ================= -->

<div class="hero-background">


<header class="hero-content">

<h1>🇳🇵 Information About Nepal 🇳🇵</h1>

<p class="sub-title">
The Wonderful Journey to Beautiful, Peaceful, and Brave Nepal
</p>

<button onclick="toggleDarkMode()" class="dark-btn">
🌙 Dark Mode
</button>

</header>



<!-- ================= About Nepal ================= -->

<section class="container card">

<h2>About Nepal 🇳🇵</h2>

<p>
Nepal is a beautiful landlocked country located in South Asia.
It is famous for Mount Everest, the highest mountain in the world,
the birthplace of Gautama Buddha (Lumbini), rich culture,
ancient temples and adventure tourism.
</p>

</section>




<!-- ================= Interactive Map (NEW) ================= -->


<section class="container card">

<h2>🗺️ Explore Nepal Map</h2>

<p>
Click the markers to explore famous places of Nepal.
</p>

<div id="nepalMap"></div>

</section>





<!-- ================= Main Content ================= -->


<main class="container main-grid">



<!-- Places -->

<section class="column card">


<h2>📍 Places to Visit</h2>



<div class="place-item">

<a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Kathmandu,Nepal" target="_blank">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544735716-392fe2489ffa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
class="place-img"
alt="Kathmandu">

</a>


<h3>
<a class="map-link"
href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Kathmandu,Nepal"
target="_blank">

📍 Kathmandu

</a>
</h3>


<p>
Capital city of Nepal famous for Durbar Squares,
Pashupatinath Temple and Swayambhunath.
</p>


</div>





<div class="place-item">


<a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Pokhara,Nepal" target="_blank">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605649487212-47bdab064df7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
class="place-img"
alt="Pokhara">

</a>


<h3>
<a class="map-link"
href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Pokhara,Nepal"
target="_blank">

📍 Pokhara

</a>
</h3>


<p>
Beautiful lakeside city with Annapurna mountain views.
</p>


</div>





<div class="place-item">


<a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Muktinath,Nepal" target="_blank">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1627894483216-2138af692e32?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
class="place-img"
alt="Muktinath">

</a>


<h3>
<a class="map-link"
href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Muktinath,Nepal"
target="_blank">

📍 Muktinath

</a>
</h3>


<p>
A sacred pilgrimage site for Hindus and Buddhists.
</p>


</div>


</section>






<!-- Trekking -->

<section class="column card">


<h2>🥾 Trekking Destinations</h2>



<div class="place-item">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585141973474-05bf99201f16?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
class="place-img"
alt="Everest">


<h3>
🏔️ Everest Base Camp
</h3>


<p>
World famous trekking route to the base of Mount Everest.
</p>

</div>





<div class="place-item">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528164344705-47542687000d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
class="place-img"
alt="Annapurna">


<h3>
🏔️ Annapurna Circuit
</h3>


<p>
Amazing trek with mountains, villages and cultural experiences.
</p>

</div>





<div class="place-item">


<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
class="place-img"
alt="Langtang">


<h3>
🏔️ Langtang Valley
</h3>


<p>
Beautiful valley with glaciers and Tamang culture.
</p>


</div>


</section>







<!-- Weather -->


<section class="column card">


<h2>🌤️ Weather Guide</h2>


<p>
Click season to see travel information.
</p>



<button class="weather-btn"
onclick="showWeather('spring')">

🌸 Spring

</button>


<button class="weather-btn"
onclick="showWeather('monsoon')">

🌧️ Monsoon

</button>


<button class="weather-btn"
onclick="showWeather('autumn')">

🍁 Autumn

</button>


<button class="weather-btn"
onclick="showWeather('winter')">

❄️ Winter

</button>




<div id="weather-info-box"
class="weather-info-display">

</div>



<button class="weather-btn"
onclick="showTip()">

💡 Travel Tip

</button>


<div id="tipBox"
class="weather-info-display">

</div>


</section>



</main>






<!-- ================= Nepal Facts ================= -->


<section class="container card">


<h2>📚 Nepal Facts</h2>


<ul>

<li>Capital: Kathmandu</li>

<li>Currency: Nepalese Rupee</li>

<li>Highest Peak: Mount Everest</li>

<li>National Flower: Rhododendron</li>

<li>Birthplace of Buddha: Lumbini</li>

</ul>


</section>






